  [Text] Buenos Aires, 22 Apr (NA) -- President Carlos Menem 
met with Belgian Prince Philippe and a Chinese Communist Party 
[CPC] delegation headed by senior official Hu Jintao this 
morning at the Olivos Residence. 
  The CPC delegation was received at the residence's main 
chalet by President Menem; Eduardo Bauza, the secretary general 
