Robert Urbain, the Belgian foreign trade and European affairs 
minister, and Marc Serbotte, the Belgian Foreign Trade Office 
ambassador. During this meeting, Menem was joined by Foreign 
Minister Guido Di Tella and Argentine ambassador to Belgium 
Victor Massuh. 
  The president and Prince Philippe took advantage of the 
sunshine to stroll in the gardens of the residence. 

