<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    De Greiff: Government `Subservient' to United States </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2404022494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
A in Spanish 0130 GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2404022494 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Canal 
A </F>

<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


