<H3> <TI>   Texaco Raises Fuel Prices Twice in Less Than 12 Hours </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Texaco Raises Fuel Prices Twice in Less Than 12 Hours </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2304173294 Mexico City NOTIMEX in Spanish 0341 GMT 23 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2304173294 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City NOTIMEX </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tegucigalpa, 22 Apr (NOTIMEX) -- Fuel prices in 
Honduras changed twice in less than 12 hours, official sources 
have reported. 
  Texaco changed its prices on the morning of 22 April, but in 
the afternoon it incorporated the changes that had been decided 
by the three other fuel distributors. 
  Texaco had set the price of premium gasoline at 10.19 
lempiras ($1.40), regular gasoline at 9.57 lempiras ($1.31), and 
diesel fuel at 7.27 lempiras ($1) a gallon. 
  Nevertheless, the local enterprise DIPPSA [Petroleum 
Products 
Distributor Corporation] and the multinational companies Esso 
and Shell decided to change their prices effective Saturday. 
  The new price structure per gallon (3.785 liters) is as 
follows: 


---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Seller        |Fuel Type     |Prior Price   |New Price     |New Price in  | 
|              |              |              |              |dollars       | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Texaco        |Premium (in t-|10.19         |10.26         |1.41          | 
|              |he morning)   |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Regular (in t-|9.57          |9.64          |1.32          | 
|              |he morning)   |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Diesel (in th-|7.27          |7.34          |1.00          | 
|              |e morning)    |              |              |              | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Esso          |Premium       |10.10         |10.38         |1.42          | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Regular       |9.49          |9.77          |1.34          | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Diesel        |7.19          |7.44          |1.02          | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|DIPPSA        |Premium       |10.10         |10.40         |1.43          | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
