---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|              |Diesel        |7.19          |7.54          |1.03          | 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  Economy Ministry authorities have said that starting 23 
April, people will have to "learn" to live with these kinds of 
changes, which will be determined by supply and demand. 

