<H3> <TI>   Government Guarantees Embraer's $172-Million Debt </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Guarantees Embraer's $172-Million Debt </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY2604002394 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 
2200 GMT 25 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY2604002394 </F>
<F P=104>  Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network </F>
<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] President Itamar Franco has signed a provisional 
measure that empowers the federal government to guarantee a Bank 
of Brazil $172-million loan to the Brazilian Aeronautics Company 
[Embraer]. The loan will be used to increase Embraer's capital 
through the issuance of new regular shares that will be endorsed 
by the federal government. 

</TEXT>

