<F P=104>  Lima Global de Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Starting her official visit to Peru, Colombian 
Foreign Minister Noemi Sanin de Rubio today met Foreign Minister 
Efrain Goldenberg. She later met President Fujimori at 
Government House. 
  [Begin recording] [First unidentified reporter] During the 
first day of her official visit to Peru, Foreign Minister Noemi 
Sanin de Rubio met at the Foreign Ministry building with her 
Peruvian colleague, Efrain Goldenberg. 
  From the Foreign Ministry building, Rubio walked to San 
