<H3> <TI>   Agriculture Minister Highlights UBPC Potential </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Agriculture Minister Highlights UBPC Potential </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL2604155494 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 0900 
