  [Text] Alfredo Jordan Morales, minister of agriculture and 
a Politburo member, has said in Bayamo that Basic Cooperative 
Production Unit [UBPC] workers are capable of developing many 
more initiatives to solve problems. Jordan, who participated in 
the initial phase of the Miscellaneous Crops National Council 
held in Granma, pointed out that the UBPCs have to be helped and 
supported; in this connection, he stressed the importance of 
housing construction. Jordan announced that the agriculture 
