<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Liberal Candidate Samper's Treasurer Killed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA2804010094 Madrid EFE in Spanish 2309 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> PA2804010094 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid EFE </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Medellin, Colombia, 27 Apr (EFE) -- Police report 
that Isabel Cristina Gutierrez de Rios, treasurer of the 
presidential campaign of Liberal Party [PL] presidential 
candidate Ernesto Samper Pizano, was killed today in this 
northwestern Colombian city. An official source said Gutierrez 
de Rios was killed in a restaurant in El Poblado, which is in 
the southwestern part of Medellin. She was attacked by 
unidentified individuals who opened fire and fled. Spokespeople 
for the presidential campaign of Samper Pizano in Medellin said 
that, after the luncheon, the treasurer was scheduled to preside 
over a meeting of the finance committee of the PL candidate. 

</TEXT>

