<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Five Shining Path Members Killed in Ucayali Clash </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY2704032094 Lima Global de Television Network in Spanish 
0130 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>

