  [Text] Hasan Ruhani, vice speaker of the Iranian [Islamic] 
Consultative Assembly, has said that the Iranian parliament 
intends to create a friendship with Cuba group. He made this 
statement during a friendly meeting with Cuban Ambassador to 
Iran Enrique Trujillo. 
